long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,es_419,et,fa,fi,:
Description:

Get ready for a heart-pounding, spine-tingling experience like no other in "Five Nights at Freddy's 3"! The third installment of this iconic horror game series takes you back to Freddy Fazbear's Pizza, but this time, the terror is more intense, and the mysteries are even darker.

Gameplay:

You play as a brave night security guard tasked with surviving five horrifying nights in this abandoned and decaying establishment. Your only tools are a monitor system, limited power supply, and your wits. Can you survive the onslaught of vengeful animatronic monsters that lurk in the shadows?

New Features:

Phantom Animatronics: Beware of the eerie and ghostly appearances of the Phantom animatronics, who will jump-scare you when you least expect it. Keep your nerves steady as you try to fend them off while conserving your precious power.

Springtrap: The nightmarish animatronic, Springtrap, is on the loose, and he's out for revenge. He's a cunning adversary, and you must use your skills to avoid his deadly traps while keeping an eye on him through the cameras.

The Horror Attraction: Experience a brand new setting in the form of "Fazbear's Fright: The Horror Attraction." Traverse its eerie corridors and terrifying rooms, each harboring its own secrets and dangers.

Minigames: Dive deeper into the lore of the Fazbear franchise by uncovering hidden mini-games that shed light on the dark history of Freddy Fazbear's Pizza.

Immersive Horror:

"Five Nights at Freddy's 3" pushes the boundaries of fear, immersing you in a nightmarish world filled with tension, anxiety, and terror. The game's chilling atmosphere, haunting soundtrack, and jump-scare moments will keep you on the edge of your seat.

Can You Survive?

As the story unravels and the horrors intensify, can you endure the relentless onslaught of the animatronics and survive until the morning light? "Five Nights at Freddy's 3" will test your nerves, your strategy, and your will to live. Can you conquer your fears and make it through the five nights?

Get ready for a gaming experience that will haunt your dreams and challenge your courage. Face your fears and dive into the madness of "Five Nights at Freddy's 3." Can you survive the night?

HOW TO PLAY
You can play with mouse.

HOW TO INSTALL
Click download this Extension using the "Add to Chrome" button.

Once the game has finished loading, simply select the "Extensions Icon" button. 

After clicking this, you'll be directed to the playground area, where the game "Tanuki Sunset Online Unblocked" will launch automatically. All that's left is to press the play button and start enjoying the game.
